# 6th Floor Fit-Up Tender Announcement

**Official Title**: Réaménagement du 6e étage / 6th Floor Fit-Up

**Reference Number**: WS4220358800 - Doc4220392028

**Solicitation Number**: WS4220358800

## Tender Details

* **Tender Status**: Expired
* **Tender Closing Date**: October 19, 2023, 14h (2:00 PM ET)
* **Expected Contract Start Date**: N/A
* **Expected Contract End Date**: January 12, 2024

## Tender Information

* **Procurement Category**: *CNST
* **Procurement Method**: Competitive - Open bidding
* **Selection Criteria**: Lowest Price
* **Trade Agreements**: *Canadian Free Trade Agreement (CFTA)
* **Regions of Opportunity**: N/A

## Contracting Entity

* **Contracting Entity Name**: Department of Public Works and Government Services (PSPC)
* **Contracting Entity Address**: 11 Laurier St, Phase III, Place du Portage, Gatineau, Quebec, K1A 0S5, Canada

## Contact Information

* **Contact Name**: Nabil Boujenoui (SPAC/PSPC)
* **Contact Email**: nabil.boujenoui@tpsgc-pwgsc.gc.ca
* **Contact Phone**: N/A
* **Contact Fax**: N/A

## Tender Description

The Department of Public Works and Government Services (PSPC) invites you to submit a proposal for the 6th Floor Fit-Up project located at 555 Mackenzie, Ottawa, Ontario. The work must be completed within 12 weeks from contract award.

**Important Note**: Please disregard the Ariba Discovery posting response deadline closing time and CanadaBuys posting closing time. All required supporting documentation and bid submission must be submitted by October 19, 2023 at 14h (2:00 PM ET). All bids submitted after the deadline will be deemed non-responsive.

To request information or clarification on the bid solicitation, please communicate with the Contracting Authority through the “Event Messages” tab within CanadaBuys (SAP Ariba). Failure to comply with this requirement may result in the bid being declared non-responsive.
